                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18101031-32-off192 t18101031-32-cd193"></join>, three bottles, value 1 l. 10 s. four snuff boxes, value 1 l. 7 s. four silver boxes, value 2 l. four purses, value 10 s. five tooth-picks, value 5 s. a tongue scraper, value 2 s. two work boxes, value 1 l. 10 s. three pair of buckles, value 9 s. nine brushes, value 1 l. 8 s. thirteen thimbles, value 13 s. three knives, value 15 s. a pair of salts, value 2 s. 6 d. and two pencil cases, value 5 s. the property of 
                     
