                     <interp inst="t18101031-32-verdict197" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               of stealing, to the value of thirty-nine shillings only
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18101031-32-punish198" type="punishmentDescription">
